{"TopicId":220421,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"Move Abort action button to the top","CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-28T21:21:58Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-28T21:21:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease move the Abort action button to the top of the list, before Brakes - to improve position logic and to prevent pressing it when activating the Science toggle or the Solar Panels.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Screenshot-2023-10-29-001731.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022185.71\u0022 height=\u0022247\u0022 width=\u0022133\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/596TDgT/Screenshot-2023-10-29-001731.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nPS: Also add a hotkey for Abort please (was Backspace in KSP1 ofc).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-10-28T21:22:39Z\u0022 title=\u002210/28/2023 09:22  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Oct 28\u0022\u003EOctober 28, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Vl3d\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-29T10:12:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPeople are using abort button?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-29T10:39:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224334854\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022220421\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221698574324\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n27 minutes ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPeople are using abort button?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat good is this question when we know people are going to use it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224334740\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022220421\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221698528118\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219348\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vl3d\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, Vl3d said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease move the Abort action button to the top of the list, before Brakes - to improve position logic and to prevent pressing it when activating the Science toggle or the Solar Panels.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u002B1\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGiven that people usually wire it to do something that ends the mission I.E. escape boosters and parachutes, it should probably tuck itself away until mouseover as well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-29T10:53:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI forgot some play with no revert option\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEh, I guess? In any case, the hotkey in emergency situation is quicker than dragging the cursor to a small button.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-29T10:56:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224334856\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022220421\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221698575985\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022182413\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bej Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, Bej Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGiven that people usually wire it to do something that ends the mission I.E. escape boosters and parachutes, it should probably tuck itself away until mouseover as well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDear God no. The last thing I need is to move my mouse over the lights icon, and right as I click the abort icon pops up instead.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-29T11:46:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224334859\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022220421\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221698577018\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Superfluous J\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n49 minutes ago, Superfluous J said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224334856\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022220421\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221698575985\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022182413\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bej Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Bej Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGiven that people usually wire it to do something that ends the mission I.E. escape boosters and parachutes, it should probably tuck itself away until mouseover as well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDear God no. The last thing I need is to move my mouse over the lights icon, and right as I click the abort icon pops up instead.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI meant it like in KSP 1, it pops out to the side or from the top. Why would I suggest that it \u003Cem\u003Eoverlaps\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0another button?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Abelinoss","CreatedById":222638,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-29T13:01:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd an abort hotkey: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/219340-abort-hotkey-not-present/#comment-4320041\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/219340-abort-hotkey-not-present/#comment-4320041\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}